DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T220000
SUMMARY:Tuesday Boardgames Evening at Mox Boarding House
DESCRIPTION:Portland 20s-30s: Coffee\, Bars\, & Hiking!\nHi everyone!\nLet’s continue our board game evenings! The location for this meetup is:\n\n📍 **Mox Boarding House**\n🕕 **6:00 PM – 10:00 PM**\n📫 **1938 W Burnside St\, Portland\, OR 97209**\n\n**Spots are limited** since we don’t have a reservation. Mox offers a free game library you can enjoy along with their food and cocktails.\n\nTo help keep things organized\, please follow these guidelines:\n1. **Be punctual at 6:00 PM** so we can gather as a group and grab a large table. If you’re planning to arrive later\, please allow someone else to take your spot\, you’re still welcome to come\, but seating might be limited.\n2. **Update your RSVP** if you can’t make it. This helps others on the waitlist get a chance to join.\n\nFeel free to bring your favorite games! Drop a comment to let us know what you’re bringing or want to play.\n\nI’ll be bringing:\n• Secret Hitler\, Herd Mentality\n• Monikers\, kings of Tokio\, Tsuru\n• Bang!\, Bamboozled and few more!\n\n🍻 **Optional After-Plan:**\nFor those who want to keep the night going\, we sometimes roll over to **Wildwood Saloon** (just nearby) for a **drink\, karaoke**\, or a **round of pool**. Totally optional\, but always a fun way to close out the evening!\n\nSee you soon!\n\n📲 **Follow our IG to spot yourself in a blurry group photo!**\n👉 https://www.instagram.com/pdxoutandabout?igsh=aGlpeXFvZnVxYWNv&utm_source=q
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-2030-coffee-bars-and-hiking/events/312757943/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260106T232327Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260106T232327Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/6/b/8/f/600_531807535.jpeg
END:VEVENT
