SUMMARY:Senses Band Show
DESCRIPTION:Portland 20s-30s: Coffee\, Bars\, & Hiking!\nCome join us for some fun live music by Senses the band!\n\nhttps://music.youtube.com/channel/UCW7I-b53NStOYhyP50kn5hA?si=Jeciat0VTqIlec4H\n\nTicket Information can be found at:\nhttps://www.etix.com/ticket/p/84876641/the-summer-set-portland-hawthorne-theatre?clickref=1101lC86tVjI&clickref=1011lC8sJSPT&app_clickref=1011lC8sJSPT.\n\nParking: the best options are often on the side streets behind the theater (towards SE 38th or 40th Ave) or in the neighborhood between Hawthorne Blvd and Division St.
